(10, 59, 7, 45, 'Smart Axiata Company Limited (Smart)', '500', 'smart', '09666152452', '0125425', 'jobs@smart.com.kh', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.smart.com.kh', 'Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '<p>Smart Axiata Company Limited became a subsidiary of Axiata Group Berhad (Axiata) after it entered into a strategic merger with Hello Axiata Company Limited. The merger has resulted in the creation of the leading mobile telecommunications company in Cambodia with more than eight million subscribers.</p>\r\n', '28c05b4fc30ba14dde0138521115de81.png', '', 'null', '', 0),
(14, 56, 7, 45, 'Aseanhr', '>9', 'HR department', '095 666 716', '095 666 716/093 220 978', 'rinphanit6666@gmail.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.aseanhr.com', '#16, Olympia City, Sangkat Boueng Prolit, Khan 7 Makara, Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '<p><b>ASEANHR</b> is the most popular jobsite specializing in providing jobs vacancies and high qualification human resource to our partners. We have grown from specializing in online jobs advertising, recruitment and sourcing employees of all standards for businesses and organizations across the Asia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'e40b695fd7e9b3b2f351910eebd7c0b3.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(15, 40, 7, 45, 'Corarl Co., Ltd', '>11', 'HR department', '089 222 055/ 93 220 978', '023', 'work@corarl.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.corarl.com', 'Olypia City, #S16-18, Sangkat Boueng Prolit, Khan 7 Makara, Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '<p>CORARL is a startup company focusing on cloud technology in developing cloud talent management system. In order to deliver a robust, user-friendly, and efficient system to our clients</p>\r\n', '0e43e98cecc4fe4c396479d33edf9b71.png', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(16, 50, 7, 45, 'Mekong Garden', '>100', 'HR department', '081/066 67 21 91/023 69 59 635', '023 69 59 635', 'hr@mekong-gardens.com', '25d55ad283aa400af464c76d713c07ad', 'www.mekong-gardens.com', 'Road 6A, Chroy Changvar, Russey Keo, Phnom Penh, Kingdom of Cambodia. T: +855 (0) 23 69 59 635, E: Info@mekong-gardens.com', '<p>ឧទ្យានមេគង្គ<br>\r\n	ឧទានមមគង្គ គឺជាសណំ ង្់ថីមម ួយ ដដលចាប់មផើមត ដមំណើ រការអាជីវកមរម បស់ខ្ួនល មៅកុង្ន ឆ្ន ំ ២០១១ មរកាមគមំ ោង្<br>\r\n	ហរញ្ិ ញបបទានរបស់ធនាគារកាណាឌីយ៉ា ក.អ ដដលមានអាផាតដមនចនំ ួន១៤៦បនបទ ់។ មដើមបមី ្ើយល តបនឹង្តរមូវការនន<br>\r\n	ការរកី ចមំ រនើ បចុបច បនមន នេះមយើង្ខ្ុរំ្ តូវការមរជើសមរសើ មបកជខ នទាង្ំ ពីរមភទ ដដលមានសមតភាថ ពសាក់សម កុង្ន ការបមំ ពញ<br>\r\n	ការងារដដលមានតួនាទីដូចខាង្មរកាម៖</p>\r\n', 'e3290c9f2b7ab88ca4421d2b82fa4ef0.png', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(17, 59, 8, 45, 'Kingtel Communications Limited', '50-100', 'Mr. Kevin', '098 77 39 01', '', 'careers@kingtel.com.kh', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.kingtel.com.kh', '		#728-734, Kampuchea Krom Blvd (#128), Sangkat Boeung Rang, Toulkrok District, Phnom Penh', '<p>KINGTEL is a new telecommunications company with ambition to lead the market by providing state-of-art and latest telecommunications services through 4G LTE Plus.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	KINGTEL is an operation company which holds Licenses for 4G LTE with 2.5-2.7GHz spectrum, ISP, E-Data Centre.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	KINGTEL has planned to build nationwide 4G LTE Network, IDC, and 100Gbps Nationwide Optical Transmission Network.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	KINGTEL is providing 4G LTE Plus Data Access with most reliable and affordable service packages.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	KINGTEL will offer people of Cambodia new experience of high-speed broadband Internet access most of the time</p>\r\n', 'dad907988c410382994b05061fd66825.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(18, 21, 8, 45, 'Rui Feng(Cambodia)International co.,ltd', '<10', '李小姐', '李小姐012 822 292', '', 'hr@rfsugar.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.hengfusugar.com', 'Preah Vihear', '<p>我们是中国十大糖业里的第四大集团公司旗下的公司，目前在金边与柏威夏设立办公室，于柏威夏省正在建设工厂，未来有很大发展空间。</p>\r\n', 'b503b12fcdb82124a66131baec656382.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(19, 50, 8, 45, 'NOYAKONG GROUP CO., LTD', '>100', 'Mr. Chea Sarith', '+ 855 89 333 538', '', 'recruit@noyakong.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.noyakong.com', 'Headquarters No. S116-S117, Olympia City, Sangkat Boeung Prolit Khan 7 Makara, Phnom Penh, Cambodia.', '<p>Noyakong Group Co., Ltd (NYK) is a highly-specialized company distributing products and services in Cambodia. We are a young, dynamic, and dedicated team building technical competencies to provide advanced products and services in specialized sectors including agro-industrial, healthcare, and industrial equipment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The company consists of a highly specialized and experienced team of engineers. This team focuses on the core designing, planning, and consulting of the projects. Our core value is the return-on-investment of our customers&rsquo; projects.</p>\r\n', 'f71a01f51847070dde1be33e2b4e3809.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(20, 23, 8, 46, 'PRIME MF Microfinance', '100-200', 'HR/Admin Dept', '023 993 905/023 993 910', '', 'hr@primemf.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.primemf.com', '#A19, St.271, Sangkat Tomnob Tek, Khan Chamkarmorn, Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '<p>Prime MF Microfinance Institution Ltd. is a professional licensed microfinance institution with a mission to provide financial services to individuals and groups in Cambodian communities to help them liberate from poverty.&nbsp;<br>\r\n	The MFI was registered with the Ministry of Commerce in August 2010 as a financial service provider and obtained a microfinance institution license from the National Bank of Cambodia (NBC) in December 2010. Its operation started in the current head office located at #19A Street 271, Sangkat Tomnub Tek, Khan Chamkarmon, Phnom Penh.<br>\r\n	To ensure access to financial services for communities in broader areas, Prime MF has opened its new branch every year since 2013. The second branch was set up in Pochentong in June 2013. One year later, another branch of Prime MF was settled in Russey Keo in June 2014. Takhmao, the capital of Kandal Province, was selected as the base of the fourth branch and opened in June 2015. In August 2016, the fifth branch in Angk Snuol started its operation.<br>\r\n	Prime MF is a well-known provider of microfinance service in Phnom Penh with its flexible and speedy process. It has fulfilled its commitment by increasing loan portfolio with affordable products and quality financial performance.<br>\r\n	At present, its total loan outstanding has reached to USD 11 million and its total asset is USD 12 million.</p>\r\n', '71bdd97314247e8bc88814c285b89679.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(22, 44, 8, 45, 'Prudential (Cambodia) Life Assurance Plc.', '>200', 'HR department', '(855) 23 964 555', '(855) 23 964111', 'pclarecruitment@prudential.com.kh', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.prudential.com.kh', 'Phnom Penh Tower, 20F, #445 Monivong Blvd, Boeung Prolit, 7 Makara, Phnom Penh', '<p>Prudential (Cambodia) Life Assurance PLC began operations in Cambodia in January 2013. It is the leading life insurer in Cambodia with more than USD280 million assured and 27,000 policies issued (as at 31 September 2015). One of the first life insurers in Cambodia, Prudential Cambodia is committed to raising the awareness of life insurance among the Cambodian people and helping them protect and secure their financial futures.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Prudential Cambodia is part of UK-based Prudential plc. Founded in 1848, Prudential plc is an international financial services group with significant operations in Asia, the US and the UK. It serves around 25 million insurance customers and have &pound;505 billion of assets under management (as at 30 June 2015). Prudential plc is listed on the stock exchanges in London, Hong Kong, Singapore and New York.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Prudential plc is not affiliated in any manner with Prudential Financial, Inc., a company whose principal place of business is in the United States of America</p>\r\n', 'e3321b74de1fefc605bf6e49dc986386.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(25, 50, 7, 45, 'Sky Precious Metals Co., Ltd', '>100', 'Mr. Sean Sorath', '(092) 650 696', '', 'seansorath@gmail.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'www.spm-kh.com', 'The Icon Building, Ground Floor, #87-EM, Phnom Penh', '<p>Sky Precious Metals Co., Ltd is a part of LCH Investment Groups. We are well-established finance house offering a wide range of financial services. Our service offerings encompass an array of financial services including leveraged foreign exchange trading, bullion trading. In building a regional investment intermediary,</p>\r\n', '86eb30446a1406e5d1350767ee939ae7.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
(26, 30, 8, 45, 'Kfour Group Ltd.', '>100', 'HR department', '(+855) 23 881 356 /(+855) 81 30 66 66/ (+855) 81 96 33 33', '', 'hr@kfourgroup.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', '', 'Kfour Tower, Building Kfour building #3-1, 4th Floor, St. 169, Sangkat Veal Vong, Khan 7 Makara, Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '<p>Kfour Group Ltd. is a biggest authorized distributor electronics products in Cambodia. To expands our operation nationwide,</p>\r\n', '53d693cbbcf9f93357509483f23c7aa9.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 0),
(27, 47, 8, 30, 'Kyungshin (Cambodia) Corp.', '>200', 'HR department', 'miseconomy@hanmail.net', '', 'miseconomy@hanmail.net', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'http://www.kyungshin.co.kr', '	Borey 3, Vihear Sour Khang Choeurng Village, Vihear Sour Commune, Khsach Kandal District, Kandal', '<p>A Korean leading automobile component (Wiring Harness) company</p>\r\n', '', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
(28, 23, 8, 45, 'FIGIX Industry', '>10', 'Mr.Sok Chanboth', '(+855) 86 65 66 44', '', 'chanboth.figix@gmail.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', '', '#09 A1 A2, St.163, Sangkat ToulSvayPrey I, Khan Chamkamorn, Phnom Penh, Cambodia', '', '', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
(29, 22, 8, 46, 'MaxxPow Co.,Ltd', '>', 'HR Department', '+855 (0)71-8888 808', '', 'work@corarl.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', '', '# 5BC, St 271, Phum 11, Sangkat Toeklaok, Khan Toul Kok, Phnom Penh City.', '<p>MaxxPow Co.,Ltd. is a diversified company invested in various business areas including, trading, and retailing.<br>\r\n	Established in 2016 as a retail shop in agricultural products, MaxxPow Co.,Ltd. has gained its ground and<br>\r\n	expertise in agricultural equipment trading including tractor tire, combine crawler, vehicle tire, disc harrow, disc<br>\r\n	plug, rotary tiller, spare parts etc. MaxxPow Co.,Ltd is an international brand leader in agricultural equipment.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
(30, 17, 7, 45, 'Bitus E&C', '>10', 'HR Department', '023 980 280', '', 'hr@bitusenc.com', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', '	http://www.bitusenc.com', 'SSN Building 4th Floor, Norodom Blvd., Sangkat Chey Chomnas, Khan Daun Penh, Phnom Penh.', '<p>BITUS E&amp;C was established in Phnom Penh, is the kingdom of Cambodia on first time 07.July.2008 with the initially principle objective of making trade, Business and investment in the commercial, construction and import export. During the past 6 years, Bitus has become one of the leading pioneers in construction sector in Cambodia.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
