(187, 55, 8, 45, 'Eastland Development(HK) Co., Ltd.', '10-50', 'Adam Ding', '0884027520', '', 'adamding@eastland.com.hk', 'e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e', 'http://www.eastland.com.hk', ' Company Des', '<p>我公司是中国上市公司粤泰股份（600393）的子公司，营业历史超过20年，业务范围主要包括房地产开发、矿业、化工、金融投资。合计完成开发各类房地产项目建筑面积超过400万平方米。在金边已经完成的项目是EASTONE，在建的项目是EASTVIEW。仍有数个项目在报审中。<br>\r\n	Ours is a subsidiary of Yuetai Holdings, a listed company in China(ticker: 600393).With a history of over 20 years operation, we have finished more than 4 million square meters of construction area in real property development. We have completed the first project in Phnom Penh and made it a service apartment(EASTONE). Our second project in Phnom Penh is EASTVIEW(close to Prince Central Plaza). We have several other projects in process of application to government.</p>\r\n', '77fe9645e49a17c824c063189fa4051e.jpg', '', 'null', NULL, 1),
