hedule for checking Virus in office<br>\r\n	 Configuring print server and sharing printers<br>\r\n	 Troubleshooting the computer problem and internet problem in office and all outlets<br>\r\n	 Monitoring DNS Server 2008, DHCP Server 2008, File Server 2008 and Mikrotik Server<br>\r\n	 Installing the Database (Mysql and Apec &hellip;)<br>\r\n	 Make Schedule backup company data<br>\r\n	 Configuring PABX system<br>\r\n	 Testing Main board, CPU, RAM, HDD and Power Supply<br>\r\n	 Installing the software and hardware<br>\r\n	 Troubleshooting with Phone, Scanners and Printers<br>\r\n	 Run the network cable and cabling when company open new branch<br>\r\n	 Configuring VNC port forwarding in Router to monitoring the clients all outlets<br>\r\n	 Configuring the ADSL Modem, Wireless Routers and Hotspot Device<br>\r\n	 Block some webs and virus in MT<br>\r\n	 Support the costumers when they meet the problem with WIFI access<br>\r\n	 Configure E-mails with Ms Outlook and Backup e-mails</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br>\r\n	<b>June 2010 until December 2011, as NOC Officer at Clicknet Co., Ltd (Wireless ISP)</b><br>\r\n	 Provide friendly response to customers on the phone or by email or chat line<br>\r\n	 Handle customer&rsquo;s complaint and/or provide first stage solution to customers or refer<br>\r\n	them to appropriate area for function<br>\r\n	 Monitoring the Network or inform to appropriate area for function<br>\r\n	 Ensure key in the complaints on Database<br>\r\n	Solution for guest and customers when they have any problem<br>\r\n	with wireless connection, Internet Card problem or other problem with the best solution<br>\r\n	 Built report when get any problem and we have done to manager<br>\r\n	Maintain and Monitor network wireless (WatchUp Gold, IP sentry, Cacti)<br>\r\n	 Design network in Hotel with network wireless broadband system<br>\r\n	 Design new network infrastructure with wireless system<br>\r\n	 Installation, Configuration and Troubleshooting with wireles