(178, 'JOB-178', 127, 55, 28, 9, 45, 6, 2, 8, 'Sales Executive ($200 - $600 + High Commission)', '.', '.', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-03-26', '2017-03-20 19:34:07', '<p>- Maximize sales and deliver the most effective and creative marketing strategies<br>\r\n	-Commit to achieve the sales target assigned<br>\r\n	-Develop and maintain report relationship with the customers and team<br>\r\n	-Effectively promote the products to customers<br>\r\n	-Conduct frequent communication with customers (By Phone call, email, making appointment...etc )<br>\r\n	-Build Strong relationship with potential clients or network Other duties assigned by manager<br>\r\n	-Product: Real Estate Development, Financial Investment</p>\r\n', '<p>- Bachelor Degree of Marketing or relevant skill<br>\r\n	-Could speak Chinese fluently is a plus<br>\r\n	-Good command in English<br>\r\n	-Good at negotiation and communication with new people<br>\r\n	-Friendly/ Outgoing/ Supportive/ Presentable<br>\r\n	-Passion and dedicated person in Sales Career,<br>\r\n	-Well known the product within media application industry and financial analysts or Real Estate<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	+Condition and Benefit<br>\r\n	-Salary rank: Competitive Salary based on experience (rank from $150 - $500) + Commission<br>\r\n	-Competitive commission &ndash; could be from $10,000 up per annum based on sale performance<br>\r\n	-Bonus during Chinese New Year<br>\r\n	-Staff Party monthly<br>\r\n	-Annual Trip<br>\r\n	-Public Holiday + Annual Leave<br>\r\n	-Insurance 24 hour coverage<br>\r\n	-Working in a good and harmonious international workplace (Singaporean/ Malaysian/ Thai team)<br>\r\n	-Join with young enthusiastic team<br>\r\n	-Be able to learn more about business and financial market within Cambodia and South East Asia</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-20', '2017-04-19', 'Ms. Suon Sivly', '099 207 308', 'recruitment@sc-capital6.com', NULL, 1, 1),
(179, 'JOB-179', 127, 55, 56, 9, 45, 6, 2, 8, 'Business Development Manager ($500 up to $1.2K)', '.', '1', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-03-26', '2017-03-20 19:39:09', '<p>The Role of the Business Development Manager<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	A Business Development Manager works to improve an organization&rsquo;s market position and achieve financial growth. This person defines long-term organizational strategic goals, builds key customer relationships, identifies business opportunities, negotiates and closes business deals and maintains extensive knowledge of current market conditions.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Business Development Managers work in a senior sales position within the company. It is their job to work with the internal team, marketing staff, and other managers to increase sales opportunities and thereby maximize revenue for their organization. To achieve this, they need to find potential new customers, present to them, ultimately convert them into clients, and continue to grow business in the future.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Business Development Managers will also help manage existing clients and ensure they stay satisfied and positive. They call on clients, often being required to make presentations on solutions and services that meet or predict their clients&rsquo; future needs.</p>\r\n', '<p>- MBA in Business is preferred.<br>\r\n	- More than 2 years experience in Real Estate Industry, and has evolved in Marketing Team/Campaign.<br>\r\n	- Great Problem Solving.<br>\r\n	- Willingness to learn and a positive person.<br>\r\n	- Have a ground understanding of Real Estate Market in Cambodia.<br>\r\n	- Sociable person<br>\r\n	- Critical Thinker<br>\r\n	- Be fluent in English Language<br>\r\n	- Chinese speaker is a plus<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	BENEFIT:&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- International training from experts.<br>\r\n	- Annual Leave, PH, Insurance<br>\r\n	- Annual Party, Trip<br>\r\n	- Bonus<br>\r\n	- Chance to travel abroad.</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-20', '2017-04-19', 'Ms. Suon Sivly', '099 207 308', 'recruitment@sc-capital6.com', NULL, 1, 1),
(180, 'JOB-180', 57, 34, 28, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'ផ្នែកលក់/Sales', '1', '10', 2, '18 ~ 35', 'High School', 'English-- Fair   ', '2017-03-22', '2017-03-20 19:44:27', '<p>- ស្វែងរកអតិថិជនថ្មីនៅក្នុងតំបន់ ដែលក្រុមហ៊ុនបានបែងចែកអោយ<br>\r\n	- ចុះជួបនិងបង្កើនទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ ជាមួយអតិថិជន<br>\r\n	- ទទួលបញ្ជាទិញពីអតិថិជន​ និងប្រមូលលុយ<br>\r\n	- រៀបចំផលិតផលអោយបានស្អាត និងពិនិត្យកាលបរិច្ឆេករបស់ទំនិញ<br>\r\n	- ធ្វើរបាយការណ៏ រឺទិន្នន័យពីគូរប្រកួតប្រជែង<br>\r\n	- ធ្វើរបាយការណ៏លក់ប្រចាំថ្ងៃ ប្រចាំសប្តាហ៏ និងប្រចាំខែ អោយប្រធានផ្នែកលក់<br>\r\n	- ចូលរួមសកម្មភាពផ្សេងៗរបស់ក្រុមហ៊ុន</p>\r\n', '<p>- បុគ្គលិកទាំងពីរភេទ<br>\r\n	- មានបទពិសោធន៏ក្នុងការលក់ពី ១ឆ្នាំឡើងទៅ<br>\r\n	- អាចប្រើប្រាស់ភាសាអង់គ្លេសបាន<br>\r\n	- មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ក្លាហាន និងគោរពពេលវេលា<br>\r\n	- មានភាពឆ្លាតវៃក្នុងការដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា<br>\r\n	- មានភាពអំណត់ និងទទួលខុសត្រូវក្នុងការងារខ្ពស់</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-20', '2017-04-19', 'Bunly Kim', '023-638-1332', 'mekongne@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 1),
(181, 'JOB-181', 57, 34, 31, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'Marketing Officer', '3', '2', 0, '25 ~ 35', 'High School', 'English-- Fair   ', '2017-03-25', '2017-03-20 19:52:57', '<p>1. Working Scopes:<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Marketing Officer monitor the company&rsquo;s marketing campaigns both internally and externally. Create campaigns and coordinate with related departments in promoting brand awareness.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	2. Responsibility:<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Create marketing campaigns and other marketing activities to build the brand awareness<br>\r\n	- Preparing, planning and managing the distribution of the marketing materials(Leaflets, Banners, Parasol, .Etc.)<br>\r\n	- Preparing and managing Advertising Schedule for advertising agency.(Media advertising, Radio, Magazine, .etc.)<br>\r\n	- Monitoring on media planning and media contract with suppliers.<br>\r\n	- Creating and developing new advertising concepts and drafting artwork to deliver the massage to the target customers.<br>\r\n	- Do the marketing budget planning<br>\r\n	- Updating and evaluating the effectiveness of all marketing activity.<br>\r\n	- Preparing research and survey to develop and implement new marketing projects and promotions.</p>\r\n', '<p>- A bachelor&#39;s degree in marketing, business administration or a similar field<br>\r\n	- At least 2 or more years of work experience of marketing<br>\r\n	- Have knowledge of a marketing concepts<br>\r\n	- Creative<br>\r\n	- excellent communication skill and negotiation<br>\r\n	- Well presented with a professional manner<br>\r\n	- Punctual, self improvement, flexible, dependable<br>\r\n	- Highly responsibility to make things done<br>\r\n	- Able to work under pressure<br>\r\n	- Able to work in team/individual<br>\r\n	- Good in problem solving</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-20', '2017-04-19', 'Bunly Kim', '023-638-1332', 'mekongne@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 1),
