(184, 'JOB-184', 132, 18, 62, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'Sales & Marketing Executive/Senior Sales (Indoor+Outdoor) -- Salary+Comm ', '2', '10', 2, '21 ~ 35', 'Others', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-03-29', '2017-03-20 20:29:03', '<p>*Position: Sales &amp; Marketing Executive/Senior Sales (Indoor+Outdoor) -- Salary+Comm $800 up<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	*Company: Media/Advertising<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Senior Sales **<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	1. Develop sales strategies.<br>\r\n	2. Manage and monitor sales teams.<br>\r\n	3. Create strong business relations with customers.<br>\r\n	4. Build up relations with existing customers.<br>\r\n	5. Find prospective customers,sales of product to customers.<br>\r\n	6. Plan and prepare sales report.<br>\r\n	7. Train, Manage and motivate the sales team.<br>\r\n	8. Can work inside and outside office.<br>\r\n	9. Other tasks as required.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Sales Executive **<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	1. Find prospective customers,sales of product to customers.<br>\r\n	2. Make a cold calling to target clients and have a face to face meeting.<br>\r\n	3. Build good relationship with clients.<br>\r\n	4. Can work inside and outside office.<br>\r\n	5. Other tasks as assigned by manager.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Email Resume: davidsunho.group@gmail.com</p>\r\n', '<p>Job Requirements:<br>\r\n	1. Male / Female.<br>\r\n	2. Any Qualification.<br>\r\n	3. Experience in Sales Industry (preferred).<br>\r\n	4. Can Speak / Write : Chinese, English, Khmer (preferred).<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Email Resume: davidsunho.group@gmail.com</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-20', '2017-04-19', 'DSPG', '096 255 8883', 'davidsunho.group@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 1),
