(186, 'JOB-186', 17, 59, 28, 9, 45, 6, 2, 8, 'Sale Executive/ Sale Supervisor/Freelancer( PP & Siem Riep, SHV & Battamba', '.', '10', 2, '20 ~ 35', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-03-22', '2017-03-21 17:02:56', '<p>Sale Executive<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	+Job Description:<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	-Performing sale action to achieve monthly target<br>\r\n	-Collaborating with Line Supervisor on customer specific requirement.<br>\r\n	-Getting customer and Introduce the product.<br>\r\n	-Increase product &amp; brand awareness through various activities.<br>\r\n	-Maintaining strong relationship with customers.<br>\r\n	-Dealing with team/ other to resolve complaints made by customers.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Sale Supervisor<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	+Job description:<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Enhancing team accomplishments and competence.<br>\r\n	- working with assigned team to achieve sale target<br>\r\n	- identifying business opportunities in vertical market by identifying prospects and evaluating their position in the industry; researching and analyzing sales options.<br>\r\n	- Contributing to the annual sales and marketing plan.<br>\r\n	- Planning and managing marketing events and evaluating their success.<br>\r\n	- Supporting Sales &amp; Marketing Manager in day to day sales &amp; marketing activities</p>\r\n', '<p>Sale Executive<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	+Job Requirement:<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	-Fresh graduated or bachelor degree in Marketing, Business, or IT is preferable<br>\r\n	-English language; Chinese is more advantages<br>\r\n	-having previous experience in sale is preferable<br>\r\n	-strong commitment &amp; working responsibility<br>\r\n	-computer skill/ MS-Office<br>\r\n	-good interpersonal skill &amp; presentation skill<br>\r\n	-can work with minimum support and supervision<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Sale Supervisor<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	+Job Requirements:&nbsp;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Bachelor degree in Business Administration, Marketing, IT or other related field<br>\r\n	- English language, Chine