(227, 'JOB-227', 140, 34, 37, 9, 45, 3, 2, 8, 'Purchasing Assistant', '.', '.', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-03-24', '2017-03-22 15:32:26', '<p>- Make cost comparison between a vendors to another vendors.<br>\r\n	- Checking on document (sale contract, PI, or Invoice) when received from Vendors.<br>\r\n	- Updated cost by vendors.<br>\r\n	- Monitor stock levels: controlling inventory levels to avoid stock-out situations.<br>\r\n	- Make Purchase Report.<br>\r\n	- Purchasing Tracking: Order date, ETD, ETA, and Payment.<br>\r\n	- Make Sale Report by brand.<br>\r\n	- Make purchase requisition and purchase order.<br>\r\n	- Other tasks required by Manager/Boss.</p>\r\n', '<p>- At least graduated bachelor degree of Business Administrative or relevant fields.<br>\r\n	- Preferable with experience in using Sage ERP Accpac 6.0 Accounting System.<br>\r\n	- Willing to learn and patient to adapt with new product arrangement.<br>\r\n	- 2 year experience involved with stock/inventory arrangement is a plus.<br>\r\n	- English proficiency</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-22', '2017-04-21', 'Mr. Chhun Roathy', '092/93 42 92 40 ', 'chhunroathy@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 1),
