(283, 'JOB-283', 146, 41, 28, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'Sales in Showroom (5).', '1', '5', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-04-22', '2017-03-24 15:48:49', '<p>**&nbsp;Purpose of position<br>\r\n	To sell products of company in showroom to achieve sales target set by sales supervisor.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Greet walk-in customers and welcome them warmly.<br>\r\n	- Provide supportive guidance to customers in order to convince them to buy the products in showroom.<br>\r\n	- Keep products in the showroom clean.<br>\r\n	- Follow up and build good relationship with existed and new customers.<br>\r\n	- Make sales daily report.<br>\r\n	- Other tasks assigned by sales supervisor</p>\r\n', '<p>-Year-two student majoring in sales and marketing or two-year diploma of sales and marketing.<br>\r\n	- One year experience is an advantage.<br>\r\n	- Speaking English is a must&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- Being friendly and strong self-motivated.<br>\r\n	- Good at communication.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** BENEFIT:<br>\r\n	NPHC Trading Co., Ltd provides candidates a competitive salary based on education, prior-experience and potentiality. We offer annual salary increase plus other benefits such as holiday entitlement, performance related bonus, 13th month salary.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** How to apply:<br>\r\n	Interested applicants are invited to submit a cover letter and CV with expected salary to the Human Resource department in contact below. (Do not attach copies of certificates to the e-mail but bring them when called for interview). Only shortlisted candidates will be invited for interview.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Contact person : HR Department<br>\r\n	- Address : # 705Eo, Monivong Blvd, Beong Keng Kong III, Khan Chamkamorn, Phnom Penh, Cambodia.<br>\r\n	- Phone Number : 016559078, 023211116<br>\r\n	- Email Address : hr@nphomecenter.com/engkimseng@gmail.com<br>\r\n	- Website : www.nphnomecenter.com<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Closing Date : April 25, 2017</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-03-24', '2017-04-23', 'HR Dep