(284, 'JOB-284', 146, 41, 28, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'Whole Sales Representative', '2', '.', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-04-22', '2017-03-24 15:54:11', '<p>** Purpose of Position: To sell products of company to the retail stores in targeted area to achieve sales target set by supervisor.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	- Introduce and sell company products to client or retailer shop.<br>\r\n	- Work with various in house and customer software system to process order, verify inventory, and provide tracking information.<br>\r\n	- Manage and develop execution of strategic sales plans and campaigns for growing whole sales business.<br>\r\n	- Build and maintain strong relationship with existed clients to ensure that high level of customer satisfaction and customer retention is accepted.<br>\r\n	- Find new clients and follow up them for products distribution.<br>\r\n	- Provide supportive idea to retailer shop by sharing and discussion to find a better solution when low sales margin occurs.<br>\r\n	- Negotiate with clients about the product price, specification, and delivery.&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- Prepare daily, weekly, and monthly sales report for sales supervisor.<br>\r\n	- Other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</p>\r\n', '<p>- Bachelor Degree in any field of relevance<br>\r\n	- At least one-year experience in related position<br>\r\n	- Can uses Microsoft word office<br>\r\n	- Be able to work flexible time<br>\r\n	- Excellent interpersonal and communication skill<br>\r\n	- Minimum 2 years of experience in B2B Sales of furniture products is an advantage&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- Good communications skills and ability to sales products&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- Be able to communicate in English<br>\r\n	- Be able to traveling around city or province&nbsp;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** BENEFIT:<br>\r\n	NPHC Trading Co., Ltd provides candidates a competitive salary based on education, prior-experience and potentiality. We offer annual salary increase plus other benefits such as holiday entitlement, perfo