(297, 'JOB-297', 148, 23, 45, 9, 24, 4, 2, 7, 'Card System Officer', '3', '.', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-04-01', '2017-03-24 16:53:42', '<p>**&nbsp;Job Description<br>\r\n	The Card System Officer is responsible for managing card system and maintaining all application related to card system for smoothly operation.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Location<br>\r\n	Phnom Penh, Head Office<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Duties and Responsibilities<br>\r\n	- Daily checking system to make sure the whole system working fine and correctly. Like checking VISA/MC/China UnionPay/E-Commerce connections and all type of transactions performed by on-us card and off-us card on our terminals and on off-us terminals.<br>\r\n	- Maintain all card system application servers connect to Oracle Database server, all application to Oracle Database.<br>\r\n	- Creating new user in system, assign user rights and install card system application on PC.<br>\r\n	- Fixed and repair some IT equipment HardWare like printer/fax error and some card system software and other office software like Install new windows, Microsoft office, Email&hellip;etc.<br>\r\n	- Create new terminal keys (POS-ATM), assigned new key into terminal and do configuration on terminal in the system.</p>\r\n', '<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;\r\n				<table>\r\n					<tbody>\r\n						<tr>\r\n							<td>-Bachelor degree in business, communications, computer science, IT or equivalent work or educational experience.<br>\r\n								3 years experience in Card System.<br>\r\n								- Good knowledge in software and systems related to Card operational management.<br>\r\n								- In-depth knowledge of Card operations, including hardware, software, communication and security.<br>\r\n								- Proficient in leadership and negotiation skills.<br>\r\n								- Strong interpersonal skills and communications skills (oral and written) in English language.<br>\r\n								- Ability to manage a complex team with unique processes a