(357, 'JOB-357', 46, 43, 28, 9, 45, 4, 2, 8, 'Sales Manager', '.', '.', 2, '.', 'Bachelor Degree', 'English-- Good   ', '2017-04-12', '2017-04-10 09:59:04', '<p>* Job description<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	Maximize performance of assigned section by management method<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	1. Determining job duties of each section and positions (keep updating continuously)<br>\r\n	2. Visualize performance of each staffs&nbsp;<br>\r\n	3. Setting KPI of each section&nbsp;<br>\r\n	4. Keeping truck of KPI record of each positions periodically&nbsp;<br>\r\n	5. Manage each performance&nbsp;<br>\r\n	6. Making the system to enhance the performance &amp; productivity of each members&nbsp;<br>\r\n	7. Communicate with all group members in order to enhance their performances&nbsp;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	1.Starting working with Director and team members in order to learn corporate philosophy and action plans(2~3 month)<br>\r\n	2.After learning about team members and clarify specialty, get promotion after discussion with board member &quot;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Business field<br>\r\n	Operated in 3 fields, (1)Trading and Distribution (2)Agricultural production and (3)Consumer Service.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	(1)Trading and Distribution &#39;&#39;LOKA Food &amp; Beverage&#39;&#39;<br>\r\n	Food wholesale business, main products are meat, fishery and ingredients for supporting horeca industries(Hotels, Restaurants and Cafe)<br>\r\n	Import directly from Japan,Thailand and Vietnam from reliable business partners&nbsp;<br>\r\n	Main market is in Phnom Penh and Sihanoukville. Siem Reap is planned to expand further provinces<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	(2)Agricultural production&nbsp;<br>\r\n	We possesses the land located in Kampot provinces for Pepper Plantation and other kinds of vegetables&nbsp;<br>\r\n	Inviting professional Japanese expert who has 30y experience in agricultural fields in Japan for supporting our plantation.&nbsp;<br>\r\n	Our aim is to produce high-quality Kampot pepper and export to all foreign countries.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	(3)Consumer service<br>\r\n	Under planning to start opening restaurant &quot;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>* Job Request<br>\r\n	(MUST）<br>\r\n	- Fluent English (Speaking , Writing , Understanding)&nbsp;<br>\r\n	- Person who understand the difference between management (manager) and leader (player)<br>\r\n	- Person who agreed with our action policy and Values&quot;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Job Request<br>\r\n	（WANT)<br>\r\n	- Work experience in food industries<br>\r\n	- Foreign language ability (Chinese/Thai/Vietnam/French&hellip;preferred)<br>\r\n	- Person who has the ability of logical thinking and like to think deeply (thinking ability is highly required)<br>\r\n	*Person who ever manage some team members and realize to enhance performance &quot;<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Hiring flow<br>\r\n	- 1st STEP : Pre-interview test<br>\r\n	- 2nd STEP : A few times of interviews<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Holiday : National holidays,18 annual leaves from 2nd year<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Benefits : Mobile phone, Lap top(if any),Company party, assessment of salary (twice per year),OT Charge,work permit etc.<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Work day : Monday to Saturday(one day off) ** Work time : 8:00-8:30～17:00-17:30<br>\r\n	<br>\r\n	** Job experience : All kinds of manager (management duties)&nbsp;<br>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', 0, 1, '2017-04-10', '2017-05-10', 'Ms. Sopheak', '023-966-313 / 089-777-653', 'kosuke.mineshima@seats-inc.com', NULL, 1, 1),
